<div class="head_titles">
<h1 class="entry-title" title="The attack on Parliament Hill and the War Memorial left one Canadian soldier and one male suspect dead">
Attack on Ottawa: PM Harper cites terrorist motive
<a href="#" class="addtowatchlist add awl-article" title="Add to ..." rel=""
id="atwlArticleTitle">Add to ...</a>
</h1>
<div class="entry-meta">
<p class="byline author vcard">
JOSH WINGROVE, STEVEN CHASE, BILL CURRY AND JILL MAHONEY
</p>
<p class="creditline source-org vcard">
OTTAWA AND TORONTO&nbsp;&#8212;&nbsp;Globe and Mail Update (Includes Correction)</p>
<div class="dateline">
<p>Published
<time datetime="2014-59-22T13:10:34Z"
pubdate>Wednesday, Oct. 22 2014, 9:59 AM EDT</time>
</p>
<p>Last updated
<time class="updated" datetime="2014-21-24T19:10:17Z"
pubdate>Friday, Oct. 24 2014, 3:21 PM EDT</time>
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</header>
<div class="entry-content fontsmall simplesans">
